citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:30 am on 05-
OCT-21. The inspector knocked on house door, made contact with licensee's wife. She stated the licensee was not home,
and there were no available representatives to accompany for inspection.
End Section
